data.description: Welcome to Morgan Farm Estates!  This beautifully maintained home is located in the highly desirable 55+ community of Morgan Farm Estates.  This bright, spacious home offers single floor living and an open concept.  The home consists of 2 spacious Bedrooms & 2 full baths. For those who love to cook, the kitchen boasts of beautiful cabinetry, granite counters with an abundance of counter space, stainless steel appliances and beautiful hardwood flooring! Or, relax with friends and family in the Living room with cathedral ceiling and large gas fireplace.  Additional features include Master suite with full bathroom and 2 large closets, Central air, deck off the back, 2 car garage with direct entry into home, first floor laundry, lots of closet space and a full unfinished basement with more storage space!  Showings to start at open house Friday 10/15.  Open houses on the following days and times:  Friday 10/15 from 4-6 pm; Saturday and Sunday 10/16 & 10/17 from 12-2.  After these dates, showings by appointment.
